title: Monoline rounded display sans (possibly custom?)
content:
I don't remember the context of this — I think it was a magazine nameplate, but a Google search turned up nothing. I quickly sketched it in my notebook to ID later, and I (crudely) recreated it in Illustrator. I think there's a good chance that it's custom, but I was wondering if anyone recognized it.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150317162228im_/http:/typophile.com/files/cuizine_5137.png)
author: DrDoc
